                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-red/10 text-brand-red rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Chimichurri</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-red/10 text-brand-red rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Papas Asadas</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-red/10 text-brand-red rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Ensalada Verde</span>
